episodes.title: Korean Celebs That Were Associated With Cults
episodes.description:
Korea is full of cults, and it's very easy to get to one there. So no wonder there are plenty of documentaries about Korean cults. They are not only trying to lure Korean netizens but also foreigners, so there are many articles and videos about how to avoid these cults and not get into their traps. So as it's so common in South Korea, it's no surprise that many Korean celebrities got involved in scandals for allegedly being a part of the cult.
